data.description: Lovely well maintained 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, home in a great location.  Eat-in kitchen separate dining room. Spacious living room, with sliding glass doors. that leads to the deck. Master bedroom huge with plenty of closet space and a full bathroom. two more sizable bedrooms sharing a hall bathroom  Finished basement with a huge bedroom and separate entertaining area.  A full bathroom., laundry and storage areas and a walk-out deck. Due to COVID-19 concerns, all parties must wear masks when viewing the home. Please refrain from using restrooms.
